Start xcore daemon :- Done
    * export STORJ_NETWORK=STORX
    * xcore daemon

Create new config if new node  :- Done
    - Fetch Wallet Address from Env
    - Fetch IP address from .env or take live IP
    - defualt size and port 
    * xcore create --storx 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 --storage /home/user/xcore --size 10TB --rpcport 12345 --rpcaddress 81.81.81.81 --noedit


Start xcore:- Done with jugad
    - again start xcore daemon even if already started
    - start xcore node with config file
    * xcore start --config /home/user/.xcore/configs/your_node_id.json
